Package csc130.KevinLi.lab4

Class ArrayStack<T>

java.lang.Object
csc130.KevinLi.lab4.ArrayStack<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Stack<T>
public class ArrayStack<T> extends Object implements Stack<T>

Title: Stack

Description: Interface for the Abstract Data Type Stack

Copyright: Copyright (c) 2023

Author:
Kevin Li This ArrayStack class represents a last-in-first-out (LIFO) stack of objects. The usual push and pop operations are provided, as well as a method to peek at the top item on the stack, and methods to test whether the stack is empty or full. When a stack is first created, it contains no items.
